{"word":"H6161 - עֲרֻבָּה - ʻărubbâh - ar-oob-baw' - Pledge - அடகு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>עֲרֻבָּה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʻărubbâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ar-oob-baw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Pledge / அடகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அடையாளம், கையடித்துக்கொடுத்தல் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"a pledge, a token, a bond, a surety, an exchanged thing"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Feminine passive participle of <a href=\"#/H6048 - עֲנַמֶּלֶךְ - ʻĂnammelek - an-am-meh'-lek/6048\">H6048</a> in the sense of a <i>bargain</i> or <i>exchange</i>; something given as <i>security</i>, that is, (literally) a <i>token</i> (of safety) or (metaphorically) a <i>bondsman: - </i>pledge, surety."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4627 - מַעֲרָב - maʻărâb - mah-ar-awb'/4627\">H4627</a>, <a href=\"#/H6148 - עָרַב - ʻârab - aw-rab'/6148\">H6148</a>, <a href=\"#/H6161 - עֲרֻבָּה - ʻărubbâh - ar-oob-baw'/6161\">H6161</a>, <a href=\"#/H6162 - עֲרָבֹון - ʻărâbôwn - ar-aw-bone'/6162\">H6162</a>, <a href=\"#/H8594 - תַּעֲרֻבָה - taʻărubâh - tah-ar-oo-baw'/8594\">H8594</a>"}]}